snippet.title: Legendary Wars 2.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
Celebrating the 2 Year anniversary of Legendary Wars. Legendary Wars 2.0 introduces new gameplay, new campaign, brand new heroes and over a dozen new monsters and vicious bosses.

Download here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/legendary-wars/id413423472?mt=8
